  "firstAcquaintance": "A half-treant slave and younger half-sister sharing the same father. She has delusional tendencies, often muttering to herself as if conversing with higher beings.",
  "personality": "Gentle and kindhearted, though she has the odd habit of conversing with imaginary beings.",
  "like": "Luminous natural objects",
  "familiarData": "Inova is one of her father's many children. After her father had a child with a treant slave and learned of the pregnancy, he discarded the treant back to the pasture. Inova was born in an environment with virtually no protection.\nShortly after birth, she was sold as merchandise. Inova suffered abuse under a cruel slave owner, developing various delusions as a defense mechanism to protect her mind.\nSince the abuse could not stop her mumbling, she was deemed defective once the slave owner found new slaves, and was sold at a low price on the slave market.\nInova is recorded as her father's 31st child.\nShe likes glowing stones, mushrooms, minerals, and similar things.",
